It has been decided that the way to order the individual rounds predictions is WTA.
Thus this should give the same single winner as Leo wants.

FIA points will be allocated.

There will be a new "bill-tlb" directory where only this method is run.

There will be 3 files in "bill-tlb" directory :

winner-takes-all-RACES
winner-takes-all-ALL
winner-takes-all-QUAL

Bill only wants RACES , so therefore Bill, just look at winner-takes-all-RACES

Others might want to see QUAL , and all the lot added together.



Their will be one Total FIA Points table shown at the top.
