The individual rounds will be shown below, with the most recent round, at the top of the file.

Then decision the comes on what format to output the individual rounds :

Format 1.
---------

Below the Exact matches are in CAPS.
A Prediction that is just 1 place out like Bware's PER is "Per"
Any larger error and it is all lower case.
The complicated numbers are still being calculated underneath it all, and sorting the results.


